靚自己個招牌<br />\n膠袋稅我已經好睇唔過眼<br />\n而加仲嚟多獲cut飲筒?!<br />\n你環保埋我個份啦咁<br />\n我唔支持環保啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeaff91652f9517fa9d4d7df46b7ec6862da2386","tid":958774,"uid":207563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2ca6106931b802ced885acc83d29f2aae9bea6e","tid":958774,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38613c9f7949c75dca8fe0927620d622afba0866","tid":958774,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:55:06.000Z","msg":"俾枝紙飲管都得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:02:48.000Z","msg":"珍惜樹木啊<br />\n之前果代就叫人唔好斬樹 會太多CO2 green house effect所以保護環境就要節約用紙<br />\n但呢一代環保既定義變左得返走塑...真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塑果方面 用返biodegradable既塑料都可以relieve個問題啦 但森林無左就無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"近年的確係少左人講珍惜紙張，因為木材資源漸漸都已經做到sustainable，北歐國家係例子"},{"pid":"1f6b4cfee1f8925d391393bf25f6ebfe026ce980","tid":958774,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d57477131e798366b0793420869a8fa0a3a7d172","tid":958774,"uid":25758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ef4f9882285dceaaf459fa75c72a2d4ba67fd14","tid":958774,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da1b1d2985941802cd2a7c6751ad67bd9e4d67cf","tid":958774,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"呢位巴打咪心水清"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:58:45.000Z","msg":"睇到好撚多人睇完你第一個post就開始屌鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該都係學生哥黎 多數學生思維都係咁 環保對環境好 做多好過唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好純真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但學生哥們 如果你4R 淨係講reduce拎唔到滿分架 起碼都講埋replace 會多D分架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"細路係唔識睇成個big picture<br />\n全部都冇視野<br />\n仲要佔會員大多數<br />\n依家討論po我都少入<br />\n睇完都係得啖笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"無人話過環保唔應該做<br />\n而家係個方法出左問題<br />\n但你地邏輯係出問題都要迎難而上 硬食<br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日諗呢D係第一步 之後慢慢會變好 袋左先<br />\n太多幻想啦<br />\n垃圾分類都做左好多年啦<br />\n之前又話分埋玻璃<br />\n講左幾年又係無乜聲氣<br />\n之後仲俾人踢爆埋好多垃圾分類完最後都係去堆填區既<br />\n政府自己又唔做 又要外判出去做 外判出去又唔嚴格監管 <br />\n香港搞環保真係SAI鳩氣<br />\n<br />\n有理想係好既<br />\n你可能會諗 如果每個人都好似你咁諗 又合作 咁一定會做到減塑<br />\n但係商家佬眼中 佢只係覺得佢地成功教育到班食客去幫佢節省成本<br />\n其實結果黎講唔係WIN WIN黎架<br />\n唔係WIN WIN 俾人搵笨柒 咁食客做乜要支持<br />\n而家我地提個alternative方案 又唔得<br />\n上面有巴打話如果要隻金屬羮又要洗所以又唔環保喎<br />\n即係而家擺明俾人禁住砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59208f87e57377cf0c72dba3cace9205e0c3a14e","tid":958774,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:24:26.000Z","msg":"由膠袋畀5毫已經開始覺得on9，宜家又興埋走飲管。認真唔反對環保，但班柒頭環保撚咪𨶙日夜吹奏齋走，畀啲建設性意見有乜替代方案！<br />\n<br />\n唔用膠袋！用再造紙袋得唔得？唔用膠飲管，用粟米渣造嘅得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n認真問班環保閪着草鞋𠺢？！"},{"pid":"f5a8807c29d69d4c257a2899f912eaa09aa61824","tid":958774,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ececfb8cdbcb2188eb9829a82c23dc2176014d25","tid":958774,"uid":207563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adc89527ac74ecab4f825fc028bf14e34a020eb1","t